{"tid":1622982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩先同黃絲老母一番對話","createTime":"2019-10-04T17:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:42:30.000Z","uid":22440,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3cfcef68fce037598896f29435e374223b76dcb4","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：依家美國都插手落黎啦，又咁多外國報紙報香港情況，證明左淨係宣傳比外國知，等佢地幫手咪算數lor, 班後生咁樣衝擊社會，萬一比人拉左，成世人就玩完，點解咁蠢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁呢場革命係我地ga, 你自己都唔去爭取 去打，下下靠人地幫，人地革命定你革命啊？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：就算係出去，行下企下夠鐘咪閃lor，做咩仲要返轉頭比人拉，你睇下，日日咁搞，人地果邊大把武警幫手接更，你地一個二個唔係攰就傷，點解咁唔識諗？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：首先手足返轉頭唔係蠢 唔係博拉，返轉頭係想救果班走唔切ga手足啊....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：救？你當你地係超人啊救？係人都諗自己先啦 救<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我有事，我比人拉 你會唔會不顧一切衝去警局救我？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你傻嫁，你係我粒女，我點都會救你，阿媽幾無用，跪都跪返你返黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：所以我地會返轉頭，因為果班都係我地兄弟姊妹，媽咪爸爸，香港人唔可以再咁自私，你明唔明就係上一代自私，我地呢個社會先咁冷漠，先咁多荒謬，你出街先比手推車撞，班阿叔先咁野蠻....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我知道你會好反對我地傷曬 都不顧一切繼續企出黎，我知你會好反對我壓上畢生前途去呢場革命，我知你會話我唔成熟，唔識諗，<span style=\"color: red;\">對唔住 我太愛呢片地方 呢班人</span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你真講極都唔明，係咪想激死我？人地真係出解放軍啦.....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我愛你，但請你唔好阻止我去同大家一齊，請唔好推走我，唔好令我反感一個我愛的人<br />\n<br />\n佢依家入左房，各位我會不會語氣重左？<br />\n<br />\n岩岩發生，有假我咩都得<br />\n<br />\n我諗好多人同我依家都一樣 身邊關心我們的人開始質疑同阻止<br />\n<br />\n我地知自己做緊咩 我地都大過 好成熟<br />\n<br />\n身邊的人，你地可以支持我地嗎？<br />\n<br />\n一次咁大把？<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b5ad83e670886252b1944d209a7d9629b52da216","tid":1622982,"uid":8532,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:51:01.000Z","msg":"每個手足都係兄弟姊妹"},{"pid":"fd2c9359ee125479a22659012caf6707a5d9b374","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:52:31.000Z","msg":"真係心好攰 我好想好想你地可以不顧一切支持我地<br />\n唔好再罵我地<br />\n我地其實真係識驚 每一次都好驚好驚<br />\n手都震曬<br />\n你地一句支持<br />\n真係好重要....."},{"pid":"660f849475ae67c31438050dc069bb1fa14379fa","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:55:07.000Z","msg":"我知你地關心緊張 但係你咁重語氣<br />\n我會不由自主咁嬲 同無力<br />\n其實我係好大好大壓力<br />\n我仲要返工 受人氣<br />\n我地係part time 嫁<br />\n對面full time 不突止仲要一個二個專業訓練黎對付我地<br />\n你明唔明<br />\n我們的人生都係比人包圍緊"},{"pid":"348a0be515e96a1e9525f401d17113362dac8c93","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5ad83e670886252b1944d209a7d9629b52da216","tid":1622982,"uid":8532,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:51:01.000Z","msg":"每個手足都係兄弟姊妹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc138ebbd85b5b71ae63df16f4db7972b8ded3e","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:58:24.000Z","msg":"就算事業會發展成點<br />\n無左頭家<br />\n一生都係別人奴隸<br />\n你地到底明唔明？<br />\n你地簡簡單單的生活其實唔係得返好耐的時間<br />\n講緊係一兩個月後就會無<br />\n到時候我地無曬<br />\n邊個幫你搵返呢份生活 呢個未來？"},{"pid":"55f00d7c383b15c9e1b7e101bf22430b705859ae","tid":1622982,"uid":261478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:58:29.000Z","msg":"聽日繼續快閃突擊<br />\n我地贏在人多機動性高<br />\n係屋企步行範圍內搞<br />\n唔好依賴任何交通工具<br />\n因為隨時可能封路封鐵<br />\n唔好等有狗<br />\n快閃突擊完就轉場<br />\n攰就返屋企食飯訓教回滿血再出過<br />\n政府會好快頂唔順<br />\n認同唔該用盡任何途徑spread開去<br />\n祝大家武運亨通<br />\n<br />\nBTW如果見人偷野建議先警告<br />\n唔聽就當係鬼獅鳥左佢"},{"pid":"e95b0510f8425d1c9b9338b221fc7ded8c5b4012","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"我唔識點講 好想喊<br />\n其實我都好攰好痛<br />\n好多點解"},{"pid":"5a52c0461e78d194ffdfa132564d6c0acde0e2ee","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55f00d7c383b15c9e1b7e101bf22430b705859ae","tid":1622982,"uid":261478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:58:29.000Z","msg":"聽日繼續快閃突擊<br />\n我地贏在人多機動性高<br />\n係屋企步行範圍內搞<br />\n唔好依賴任何交通工具<br />\n因為隨時可能封路封鐵<br />\n唔好等有狗<br />\n快閃突擊完就轉場<br />\n攰就返屋企食飯訓教回滿血再出過<br />\n政府會好快頂唔順<br />\n認同唔該用盡任何途徑spread開去<br />\n祝大家武運亨通<br />\n<br />\nBTW如果見人偷野建議先警告<br />\n唔聽就當係鬼獅鳥左佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"手足一定唔會 我地餓死都唔會！"},{"pid":"8b72eac558ca04d6ef53f3c1b4f77ad4b70416d7","tid":1622982,"uid":127649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"比個抱你<br />\n你都入去攬下老母<br />\n希望你地意見唔同 都要識得包容對方"},{"pid":"1879b5db179e88cf36ea94b451d4e12a601557a9","tid":1622982,"uid":138037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:02:06.000Z","msg":"I know this feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發現好多黃絲家長都係咁"},{"pid":"ae6b9f2baf73d61314f13b0f69cf347b351a74fb","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:03:01.000Z","msg":"我純粹想搵個地方比我講曬壓住壓住的心底話<br />\n我不會自殺<br />\n但係我唔會驚死<br />\n因為我無野好輸<br />\n我無用 我廢 我差 我成日煩到人<br />\n所以我呢種廢物根本唔會比你地嚇到<br />\n呢次我唔會再驚<br />\n因為拖住我 係大家"},{"pid":"8667d5d293fcdc5db529af2de3d689d31bd76653","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b72eac558ca04d6ef53f3c1b4f77ad4b70416d7","tid":1622982,"uid":127649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"比個抱你<br />\n你都入去攬下老母<br />\n希望你地意見唔同 都要識得包容對方"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:03:40.000Z","msg":"我雙魚格仲有d嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fd4d6f736f39389ff393ca1d88f9f1191c8d48","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1879b5db179e88cf36ea94b451d4e12a601557a9","tid":1622982,"uid":138037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:02:06.000Z","msg":"I know this feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發現好多黃絲家長都係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家唔好再咁自私啦"},{"pid":"e8eae48e73bda2dfa93302e5235d6d40e8ad9ef9","tid":1622982,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"其實你老母已經好好啦⋯ 都係擔心你同其他人，唔想有人犧牲"},{"pid":"4ea3cf0f51db63bd191814117866599abd85cd4d","tid":1622982,"uid":325104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e95b0510f8425d1c9b9338b221fc7ded8c5b4012","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"我唔識點講 好想喊<br />\n其實我都好攰好痛<br />\n好多點解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:06:44.000Z","msg":"明既 我媽都係咁<br />\n即使我地既理想有幾咁偉大<br />\n作為父母都唔可能想自己既仔女受傷<br />\n<br />\n同媽媽講會保護自己 只係企後面支持<br />\n有時侯善意既謊言 大家都好過<br />\n加油 你唔孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73fe3895774a41a7a32c50e1182791aa44ca792","tid":1622982,"uid":48962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:07:18.000Z","msg":"撐你呀絲打 前幾日同淺黃老母都嘈完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢直頭同我講話同中共鬥無得鬥㗎<br />\n又話留返畀其他人做 女仔出到去又做唔到啲咩<br />\n總之就係講咗一大堆打沉人嘅嘢<br />\n雖然好灰 但出到去 見住一大班手足<br />\n為住一樣嘅目標一齊努力<br />\n唔可以頹落去！<br />\n有時覺得可以有屋企人嘅支持係bonus<br />\n就算無 都有一班同夢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b816afd3abbe81c239c0caf1c82f56b2c58cca","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:08:09.000Z","msg":"我其實知道我地可能永遠都唔會醒<br />\n或者真係要集中營相見<br />\n但係呢團火 呢份精神<br />\n你地唔明 你地想未來可以苟且咁過活<br />\n都唔介意同大陸人一樣<br />\n最緊要錢<br />\nSorry 我諗我地呢樣野真係好唔一致<br />\n就算入集中營<br />\n我諗我果日都係拖實大家<br />\n笑住咁入！<br />\n你地明唔明<br />\n點解我會笑<br />\n點解我終於識由心而笑<br />\n其實你地明唔明啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1332a6b30f465a969c1159a64bc21b762e5d47","tid":1622982,"uid":127649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8667d5d293fcdc5db529af2de3d689d31bd76653","tid":1622982,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b72eac558ca04d6ef53f3c1b4f77ad4b70416d7","tid":1622982,"uid":127649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"比個抱你<br />\n你都入去攬下老母<br />\n希望你地意見唔同 都要識得包容對方"},"citedBy":1,"repl